@startuml
title Viaverse Localized Page / Notification — Sequence Diagram

actor "Client / Web SSR" as Client
participant "API Gateway / BFF" as BFF
participant "localization-service" as Loc
participant "identity/profile" as Profile
participant "taxonomy-service" as Catalog
participant "pricing/payment config" as Pricing
database "Translation Store" as DB
queue "Outbox / Kafka" as Kafka

Client -> BFF : GET page / notification render
BFF -> Loc : resolveLocale(context)
Loc -> Profile : profile locale/preferences
Loc -> Catalog : localized category names
Loc -> Pricing : currency/tax/fee formatting
Loc -> DB : load translations + fallback
Loc ..> Kafka : MissingTranslationDetected if any
Loc --> BFF : localized DTO/template
BFF --> Client : render localized response

note bottom
localization-service coordinates language, regional config,
category labels and price formatting.
Domain services keep canonical IDs/values.
end note
@enduml
